00:00:13.349 --> 00:00:21.202
Hi! Welcome to America Edition of Aha Emi Ruchi!
We're in Atlanta

00:00:29.625 --> 00:00:39.601
So, what do you call the quick snack that you are going to make for us?
Soft Rice Crackers (Methati Chekkalu)

00:00:41.517 --> 00:00:43.897
Ingredients required to make Soft Rice Crackers

00:00:44.196 --> 00:00:52.502
Rice Flour, Bengal Gram, Onions, Green Chilli, Cumin, Salt, Oil &amp; Ghee

00:00:52.817 --> 00:01:32.254
Take a cup of rice flour, a cup of pre-soaked bengal gram, chopped onions,
 cumin, green chilli, salt for taste and a little butter

00:01:36.318 --> 00:01:41.035
Mix it well

00:01:43.124 --> 00:01:50.154
Meanwhile, take a pan and heat some oil for deep frying

00:01:58.597 --> 00:02:05.045
Add water to the mix and make a hard batter

00:02:07.298 --> 00:02:16.473
Make small patties with the mixed batter

00:02:21.018 --> 00:02:38.220
You can also add some curry leaves and some coriander to the mix if you'd like

00:02:42.163 --> 00:02:47.759
Deep fry the patties

